Long history is in every world. Several legends were in history. Heros were there in each legend. And a fate around each of them that could not be rid of.
每一个世界都有几段历史, 每一段历史都有许多传奇, 每一个传奇都有一位英雄, 每一位英雄都有一个无法摆脱的宿命.
Jack is a mysterious swordsman. He likes to travel around and enjoys adventure. No one knows where he came from, but there is a place where he has adventures.
Jack是个谜一样的剑士, 他喜欢云游四方, 喜欢冒险. 没有人知道他从哪里来, 但是, 有冒险的地方就有他的身影.

The princess of the Western Kingdom has disappeared, and everyone has searched for no results, but all the evidence points to a chilling place: the horrible magic tower in the isolated islands of the Eastern Sea. It is rumored that there is a demon's lair, and none of the explorers and desperados there can come back.
西方王国的公主失踪了, 大家搜寻无果, 但是所有证据都指向了一个令人不寒而栗的地方：东部海上孤岛中那个恐怖的魔塔. 传言那里是妖魔的巢穴, 去那里的探险家和亡命徒们没有一个能回来.

In order to save the kind, beautiful and virtuous kingdom princess, the brave people still use their own methods to go to this magical cave to find the whereabouts of the princess. Jack is no exception. He went to the magic tower alone, hoping to completely destroy this magic cave with his own martial arts.
为了救出善良、美丽而贤惠的王国公主, 勇敢的人们还是用各自的方法前往这座魔窟, 去寻找公主的下落. Jack也不例外, 他只身前往魔塔, 希望能凭借自己的武艺, 彻底捣毁这个魔窟.
